            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 10:55:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "三生製藥飆9%創近5年高   收入盈利勝預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三生製藥(01530)曾升9%，至13.08元，為2020年7 月以來高位，現升6.33%，報12.76元，連升3天。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司年報\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/767x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/01530_WEB_-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司年報\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/767x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/01530_WEB_-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司年報</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司25日晚間公佈業績，2024年盈利約20.9億元，升34.9%，每股盈利86分，派末期股息每股25港仙，派息持平。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內收入91億元，升16.5%。營收和淨利潤均超市場預期。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">毛利率較上年增約1個百分點，至86.06%；經調整的經營性EBITDA約34億元，升22.9%。於去年底，集團研發30項重點產品。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14811050-%e4%b8%89%e7%94%9f%e8%a3%bd%e8%97%a5%e9%a3%869%e5%89%b5%e8%bf%915%e5%b9%b4%e9%ab%98-%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8b%9d%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/01530_WEB__FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 10:20:52",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "蔚來曾挫逾8%   折讓近9.5%配股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蔚來(09866)今早最多挫8.14%，見29.9元，現跌7.37%，報30.15元。成交3.93億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240603_FI_source-web_09866-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蔚來官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240603_FI_source-web_09866-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：蔚來官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集團公布作價每股29.46元配售股份，較昨日收市價32.55元折讓9.49%，配售最多近1.368億股A類普通股股份，配售集資最多40.3億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14811013-%e8%94%9a%e4%be%86%e6%9b%be%e6%8c%ab%e9%80%be8-%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e8%bf%919-5%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1",
