        },
        {
            "title": "A股窄幅偏軟",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股低開後偏軟。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3372點，跌1點或0.03%。現報3370，跌3點或0.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10658，跌10點或0.09%。現報10662，蹖點或0.06%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3930點，跌2點或0.05%。現報3928，跌3點或0.09%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2145點，跌5點0.23%。現報2145，升0.36點或0.02%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14810940-a%e8%82%a1%e7%aa%84%e5%b9%85%e5%81%8f%e8%bb%9f-2",
